SIMPLE: blat
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blat
<hw>Blat</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To cry, as a calf or
sheep; to bleat; to make a senseless noise; to talk
inconsiderately.</def> <mark>[Low]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blat</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Blat
<hw>Blat</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To utter inconsiderately.</def>
<mark>[Low]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If I have anything on my mind, I have to <qex>blat</qex> it right
out.</q> <rj><qau>W. D. Howells.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blatancy</ent>⟦br⟧
